title: JRE review of MMA 60 with Forrest Griffin
description:
Forrest is now part of the team that funs the UFC performance institute. This conversation with Joe talks about what the institute is doing and how they are learning the best way to support the fighters. Forrest as usual is on form and being pretty funny. Very enjoyable podcast.
